 is the probability that the continuous variable has a value between
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

 and
\begin_inset Formula $x+dx$
\end_inset

.
 We must also replace the summation with the appropriate integral to obtain
 the following result:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
