).

\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Interferences between functional groups cause the free energy to vary as
 a function of the bond rotation angle,
\begin_inset Formula $\phi$
\end_inset

, with an energy vs.

\begin_inset Formula $\phi$
\end_inset

 curve that looks like the one shown in Figure
