\begin_inset Formula $\lambda_{z}$
\end_inset

, the extension ratio in this direction:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\align center
\begin_inset Formula
\begin{equation}
P_{z}=\frac{d(\Delta F_{d})}{d\ell}=\frac{d(\Delta F_{d})}{d\lambda_{z}}\frac{d\lambda_{z}}{d\ell}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
With
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda_{z}=\ell/\ell_{0}$
\end_inset

, we have
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{d\lambda_{z}}{d\ell}=1/\ell_{0}$
\end_inset

.
