\begin{equation}
G=k_{B}Tv_{s}\beta=k_{B}Tv_{s}\frac{<R^{2}>}{R_{0}^{2}}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
For the unswollen polymer (
\begin_inset Formula $\phi_{p}$
\end_inset

 = 1), we have G =
\begin_inset Formula $G_{0}$
\end_inset

, <
\begin_inset Formula $R_{2}$
\end_inset

> =
\begin_inset Formula $R_{dry}^{2}$
\end_inset

