\begin_inset Formula $v_{s}=v_{s_{0}}$
\end_inset

.
 The parameters that change during the swelling experiment are
\begin_inset Formula $v_{s}$
\end_inset

 and <
\begin_inset Formula $R^{2}$
\end_inset

>.
 Therefore, the change in shear modlus is determined by the change in these
