\begin_layout Plain Layout
Equilibrium Swelling
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
A general expression for the pressure difference is obtained from the first
 law of thermodynamics, using an approach that is similar to the approach
 used to determine the stresses in deformed elastic solids.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Float figure
wide false
sideways false
status open

